{"tid":1960911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中共援助「N95胸罩」 巴基斯坦：我們被騙了","createTime":"2020-04-06T12:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T15:44:39.000Z","uid":193217,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"74457fd098278290c49ebc7878ecb4b274be1cae","tid":1960911,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"日前，中共援助「鐵哥們」巴基斯坦由胸罩改造的N95口罩，巴國怒斥上當受騙，引起國際社會強烈反響。中共隱瞞導致疫情擴散全球，中共試圖以「口罩外交」扭轉國際形象，但因產品質量太差，頻頻遭到退貨，被搞的灰頭土臉。<br />\n<br />\n印度大媒體Business Standard 4月5日報導，巴基斯坦遭受中共病毒（武漢肺炎）侵襲，幾乎全國癱瘓。中共承諾對其進行「優質醫療援助」，但給的卻是「用胸罩製成的」N95口罩，對巴基斯坦沒有任何幫助。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦新聞頻道的一名女主播為此在報導中怒斥「China ne chuna laga diya」，意即「中國（中共）實際上騙了我們」。<br />\n<br />\n「號稱高質量的N95口罩，中國（中共）送的是內衣製成的口罩；接受中國醫療救助的省衛生部門也有漏洞，未經過適當檢查就把口罩送到卡拉奇（Karachi）的卡達醫院，那裡的醫生和和醫護人員稱（衛生部門）被中共當傻子耍了。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/majorgauravarya/status/1246278491735113730?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1246278491735113730&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2Fa102816663.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmajorgauravarya%2Fstatus%2F1246278491735113730%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1246278491735113730%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ntdtv.com%252Fb5%252F2020%252F04%252F06%252Fa102816663.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=6b5b5570\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmajorgauravarya%2Fstatus%2F1246278491735113730%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1246278491735113730%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ntdtv.com%252Fb5%252F2020%252F04%252F06%252Fa102816663.html&h=eae893fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/majorgauravarya/status/1246278491735113730?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1246278491735113730&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2Fa102816663.html</a><br />\n印度知名戰略專家阿里亞（Gaurav Arya）在推特分享了女主播的這段報導，引起強烈反響，並被轉發到美國社交媒體上。網友表示，「如果中國（中共）稱巴基斯坦是他們的朋友卻還這樣做，那想想他對其他國家會做什麼」、「我們想要口罩，不是胸罩」、「我們要退貨」。<br />\n<br />\n根據中共使館致巴國外交部的信中稱，這批贈送的物資包括20萬個普通口罩、2000個N95口罩、2000件防護服、5台呼吸器和2000份檢測工具。上個月末，中共還要求巴基斯坦開放兩國邊界一天，以便可以運送這些醫療用品過境。<br />\n<br />\n中共「抗疫外交」受挫<br />\n<br />\n近期，中共對外輸出抗疫物資屢屢被曝不合格，被多國退貨，重創中共「抗疫外交」。與此同時，中國假口罩在全球氾濫被曝光。根據「假冒產品報告」（<a href=\"http://thecounterfeitreport.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthecounterfeitreport.org&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=65a2c175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">thecounterfeitreport.org</a>）網站3月11日報告，3M的防偽產品團隊，在中國已發現18個生產、銷售假冒口罩的窩點。<br />\n<br />\n在中共病毒大流行期間，口罩等防護用品是前線醫務工作人員急需、可以救命的物資。但這些中國假口罩帶來「嚴重問題」，其後果可能是致命的。"},{"pid":"d5c60ec85ccfb36d9ba8a6957992f2e069931770","tid":1960911,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩變奶罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cdee34a290381f18586cb595dd4b1387ddeea2","tid":1960911,"uid":170335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"侮辱回教"},{"pid":"36dede8e747f7b5380156cd9629caa814ccf6a5f","tid":1960911,"uid":301092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"厲害了 我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奶罩變口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3615cbc099e941faa08847fa09e318913abded2e","tid":1960911,"uid":126317,"like":2,"dislike